# API Conventions

- Prefix versioned routes: `/api/v1/products`, `/api/v1/webhooks/conekta`.
- Validate every body/query with Zod; return `{ error: { code, message } }` on failure.
- Auth: verify session or HMAC before business logic; return 401/403 without leaking details.

```typescript
// GOOD: webhook handler with signature check
export async function POST(req: Request) {
  const raw = await req.text();
  if (!verifyConektaSignature(req.headers, raw)) {
    return NextResponse.json({ error: { code: 'UNAUTHORIZED' } }, { status: 401 });
  }
  const event = conektaEventSchema.parse(JSON.parse(raw));
  await paymentService.handleWebhook(event);
  return NextResponse.json({ received: true });
}
```

- Use idempotency keys for payment and order creation.
- Log `requestId`, never log full card numbers, RFC, or passwords.
